=== 體積與表面積 ===
面為正三角形且邊長為單位長的扭稜鍥形體，其體積為下列方程式的實數根<ref name="dmccooey DisdyakisDodecahedron">{{cite web | author = David I. McCooey. | year = 2015 | url = http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/SnubDisphenoid.html | title = Johnson Solids: Snub Disphenoid | publisher = dmccooey.com | accessdate = 2019-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190928082659/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/SnubDisphenoid.html | archive-date = 2019-09-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="mathworld SnubDisphenoid">{{Cite mathworld | urlname=SnubDisphenoid | title=Snub Disphenoid }}</ref>：
:<math>5832V^6-1377V^4-2160V^2-4=0</math>
對應的扭稜鍥形體體積V約為<ref name="dmccooey DisdyakisDodecahedron"/>：
:<math>V\approx 0.85949</math>
面為正三角形的扭稜鍥形體，已知扭稜鍥形體有12個正三角形面，因此其表面積A為邊長為a之正三角形面積的12倍<ref name="mathworld SnubDisphenoid"/>：
:<math>A=3\sqrt{3}a^2\approx 5.19615a^2</math>

=== 構造 ===
扭稜鍥形體可以透過將鍥形體視為二角反角柱後套用扭稜變換的結果，因此扭稜鍥形體可以視為一系列扭稜反角柱無窮序列的第一項<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.orchidpalms.com/polyhedra/snub-anti-prisms/prisms1.html | title = Snub Anti-Prisms | publisher = orchidpalms.com | author = Jim McNeill | access-date = 2019-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327041449/http://www.orchidpalms.com/polyhedra/snub-anti-prisms/prisms1.html | archive-date = 2019-03-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
